022105b7db84c8a558ee0.mp4?t=1706056063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategise your way to victory - combat skills alone are not enough!</strong></h2>Deal with random events, collect powerful loot, unlock new abilities, and unearth hidden secrets as you progress through the game. Your decisions matter, and every choice could mean the difference between survival and succumbing to the ever-present peril.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746490/extras/1ae3c982601a74a1a3511cf48e9edef8.poster.avif?t=1706056063\" width=640 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746490/extras/1ae3c982601a74a1a3511cf48e9edef8.webm?t=1706056063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746490/extras/1ae3c982601a74a1a3511cf48e9edef8.mp4?t=1706056063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746490/extras/c69439c0ee9f5fafcbf37b96069eb7aa.webp?t=1706056063\" width=640 height=40 /></span>",
